<ul><li> The alternate dimension version of Buford in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/PhineasAndFerbTheMovieAcrossThe2ndDimension" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/PhineasAndFerbTheMovieAcrossThe2ndDimension">Phineas and Ferb the Movie: Across the 2nd Dimension</a></em> doesn't have a problem with the rebellion, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CommanderContrarian" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CommanderContrarian">he just likes rebelling</a>.
